==English==

===Etymology===
The origin of the term is in reference to what the number eight (8) looks like on its side. An eight on its side has the appearance of a male dog's genitalia. 

===Noun===
'''{{PAGENAME}}'''
# {{slang}} (''golf'') The condition of scoring an eight on any one [[hole]], generally regarded as a very poor score, because the maximum number (par) for any golf hole is five.

